#: inventree_emails/core.py
msgid "Email theming"
msgstr "Habillage des e-mails"

#: inventree_emails/core.py
msgid ""
"Restyle InvenTree e-mails (low stock, account, password...) to the "
"EirSpace/Scannette look, by overriding their templates."
msgstr ""
"Restyle les e-mails d'InvenTree (stock bas, compte, mot de passe...) à la "
"charte EirSpace/Scannette, en surchargeant leurs templates."

#: inventree_emails/core.py
msgid "Scannette verification page"
msgstr "Page de vérification Scannette"

#: inventree_emails/core.py
msgid ""
"Email confirmation links open the Scannette verification page (host derived "
"from the 'inventaire' -> 'scannette' naming convention)"
msgstr ""
"Les liens de confirmation d'adresse ouvrent la page de vérification de la "
"Scannette (hôte déduit de la convention de nommage « inventaire » -> "
"« scannette »)"
